title: Bug 12428: Misleading Messages in Pull Up Refactoring
description: The Pull Up refactoring displays misleading messages that need correction.
OB:
The observed behavior in the Pull Up refactoring includes:
- Misleading messages displayed during the refactoring process.
EB: The expected behavior is to have clear and accurate messages during the Pull Up refactoring.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Run the 'Pull Up' refactoring on 'TestCase.setUp' (this copies the method to 'Assert').
2. Go to the second page of the refactoring wizard.
